  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'You are quick study.


      You''ll make a fine full-time personal
      scribe for me.'
    nextOption: I wasn't really looking for a fulltime job...
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'That''s ok, I''ll hire you anyway.


      You can work for me
      and make scrolls all day, all every day.


      It will be so much fun!'
    nextOption: I'm not sure that I want to...
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Let''s get started with your training immediately.


      Make
      me one of each type of basic scroll: Agility, Intellect, Stamina, and Strength.


      You
      can keep any extra scrolls you make for yourself.'
    nextOption: Well... I guess a little practice wouldn't hurt...
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Fantastic!


      There is a table behind me near the center of
      the camp.


      You should find writing equipment there.'
    nextOption: I'll be right back with your scrolls.
